<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CanLite Offerwall</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sora:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="/theme.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/site.css">
    <script defer data-domain="trueanalytics.online" src="https://trueanalyticz.online/js/script.js"></script>
    <style>
        .offerwall-layout {
            display: grid;
            gap: 24px;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.8fr) minmax(280px, 0.9fr);
            align-items: start;
        }

        .offerwall-card,
        .offerwall-sidebar {
            background: rgba(14, 18, 31, 0.76);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border-radius: 26px;
            padding: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
        }

        .offerwall-frame {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 78vh;
            border: 0;
            border-radius: 18px;
            margin-top: 18px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        }

        .sidebar-stack {
            display: grid;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .offerwall-stat {
            padding: 18px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .offerwall-stat strong {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .offerwall-stat p {
            margin: 6px 0 0;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
        }

        .tip-list {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 18px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
        }

        .tip-list li + li {
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        .store-link {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        @media (max-width: 980px) {
            .offerwall-layout {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="noise"></div>
<div class="site-shell">
    <main class="page">
        <section class="site-section">
            <div class="offerwall-layout">
                <article class="offerwall-card">
                    <h2>Offerwall</h2>
                    <p>Complete surveys here to earn store credits. After you pick an answer, scroll down and keep moving through the flow until the survey reaches its next button.</p>
                    <iframe class="offerwall-frame" frameBorder="0" src="https://offers.cpx-research.com/index.php?app_id=31853&ext_user_id=<%= id %>&email=<%= email %>"></iframe>
                </article>

                <aside class="offerwall-sidebar">
                    <div class="sidebar-stack">
                        <div class="offerwall-stat">
                            <span>Current balance</span>
                            <strong><%= credits %> credits</strong>
                            <p>Offer rewards are added here and can be spent from your account store.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="offerwall-stat">
                            <span>What credits buy</span>
                            <strong>Ad-free at 1 credit/day</strong>
                            <p>Private links are listed in the store at 10 credits/month, and semi-private links at 5 credits/month. Both are disabled for now.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="offerwall-stat">
                            <span>Ad-free status</span>
                            <strong>
                                <% if (adfree.active) { %>
                                    Active
                                <% } else { %>
                                    Inactive
                                <% } %>
                            </strong>
                            <p>
                                <% if (adfree.active) { %>
                                    About <%= adfree.daysRemaining %> days remaining.
                                <% } else { %>
                                    Buy time from your store whenever you have enough credits.
                                <% } %>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="offerwall-stat">
                            <span>Tips</span>
                            <ul class="tip-list">
                                <li>Survey payouts now credit your account balance instead of activating ad-free directly.</li>
                                <li>If a reward takes a bit to settle, refresh this page or check the account store again shortly after.</li>
                                <li>Your purchases are managed from the account page.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <a class="button store-link" href="/account">Open Account Store</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</div>
</body>
</html>
